page.title: 10A DAY IN MY LIFE. Page two.
page.content: {page2 A DAY IN MY LIFE. face and hands then I go to my bedroom and make my bed and do quarter of an hour guitar practice.I then realise it is eight forty so I run down stairs and put my shoes and coat on.Then we put our bags in the car we get in the car and drive to school.We go in to school and do maths and English until morning break.After break we do project work until twelve o'clock.This term our project is about Insects.At twelve o'clock we have our lunch and play time.At one o'clock we come in and carry on with our work until three fifteen when we go home.At home I watch ten minutes of television then I go upstairs and play Lego until tea time.After tea I go upstairs and play with my Lego again.Then I have a bath and then go to bed after a hard day.
